		function table.getline(lnum: string|integer, end_: string|number|table|true)
		  -> string|string[]
		```
		
		---
		
		```lua
		end_:
		    | true
		```
	**/
	static function getline(lnum:haxe.extern.EitherType<Int, String>, ?end_:Null<Bool>):String;
